Splattercannon/ Injustice:
 
Splattercannon hurried out of the room and down to the Med Lab.  He unlocked the CR chamber containing the clone and stepped back.  Injustice stumbles out, holding his head.
"What's going on?" he asks as Splattercannon grabs the smaller bot by the shoulders and drags him to speak with Unicron.

airly2000 <airly2002@...> wrote:
Unicron:

"Can't you sense it my minions???? a disturbance coming from us, 
have interfered with almost all comunication in Earth... And I 
haven't comanded it???"said with a tone what showed a restained 
anger"and my inner sensors can't feel Blacknightmare's, HellPlague's 
and Malice's Precence inside... I don't like it... You must find out 
them quick, if they are around here and sent someone to find 
Injustice... He might be useful for a task.."
